        This function removes and frees a complete Exec List including all linked
        Nodes back to memory. Both List Header and all Nodes @{b}must@{ub} have been
        allocated using @{"oAllocVecPooledA()" link "oAllocVecPooledA"} or any other OpenUtil
        function.

  @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
