                          A0

        void oFreeVecPooled (void *)

  @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
        This function frees memory allocated using @{" oAllocVecPooledA() " link "oAllocVecPooledA"}
        or any other OpenUtil function, no matter if Memory was allocated from
