  @{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
        oStrBegCase (Source, MatchString)
                       A0         A1

        STRPTR oStrBegCase (STRPTR, STRPTR)

  @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
        Check if the Source string begins with the MatchString. This function
        is case-sensitive; @{"oStrBeg()" link "oStrBeg"} is the non-case-sensitive version.
        Useful for HotKey (TAB) string completition.

  @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
        Source      - The source string which to check for MatchString at the
